OL,3,COverstretched NHS putting cancer
OL,4,Cpatients at risk, ombudsman warns
OL,6,FAn overstretched, understaffed health
OL,7,Fservice with exhausted workers under
OL,8,F"unsustainable pressure" is putting
OL,9,Fcancer patients at risk, England's
OL,10,Fhealth ombudsman has warned.
OL,12,FHe is now calling for "concerted and
OL,13,Fsustained action" from the Government
OL,14,Fto allow NHS leaders to put patient
OL,15,Fsafety first.
OL,17,FIt comes as Parliamentary and Health
OL,18,FService Ombudsman (PHSO) figures
OL,19,Frevealed 1,019 investigations relating
OL,20,Fto cancer were carried out between
OL,21,FApril 2020 and December 2023.
