OL,6,FOf the complaints, 185 cases were
OL,7,Fupheld or partly upheld.
OL,9,FThe most common issues involved the
OL,10,Flikes of treatment delays and
OL,11,Fmisdiagnosis, while the majority of
OL,12,Finvestigations involved patients with
OL,13,Flung cancer, breast cancer and
OL,14,Fcolorectal cancer.
OL,16,FOther concerns included poor
OL,17,Fcommunication in cancer care, as well
OL,18,Fas referrals, end-of life care and how
OL,19,Forganisations handled complaints.
