OL,3,COverstretched NHS putting cancer
OL,4,Cpatients at risk, ombudsman warns
OL,6,FHealth ombudsman Rob Behrens said:
OL,7,F"Everyone deserves safe and effective
OL,8,Fcare.
OL,10,F"But patient safety will always be at
OL,11,Frisk in environments that are
OL,12,Funderstaffed and where staff are
OL,13,Fexhausted and under unsustainable
OL,14,Fpressure."
