OL,3,COverstretched NHS putting cancer
OL,4,Cpatients at risk, ombudsman warns
OL,6,FThe latest figures from NHS England
OL,7,Fshowed 74.2% of patients urgently
OL,8,Freferred for suspected cancer in
OL,9,FDecember 2023 were diagnosed or had
OL,10,Fcancer ruled out within 28 days,
OL,11,Fbehind the 75% target but up from
OL,12,F71.9% the previous month.
OL,14,FHowever, analysis by the BBC published
OL,15,Flast month claimed cancer waiting
OL,16,Ftimes last year in England were the
OL,17,Fworst on record.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/15
