OL,6,FHe added: "A key part of this is
OL,7,Finvesting in the workforce, for today
OL,8,Fand for the long-term, including
OL,9,Fproviding full funding for the long-
OL,10,Fterm workforce plan."
OL,12,FJohn Eastwood, 79, was left
OL,13,F"disgusted" at the care his wife of 54
OL,14,Fyears Sandra received after going to
OL,15,FYork Hospital with abdominal pain in
OL,16,FJune 2020.
OL,18,FCT scans showed a mass in the
OL,19,Fgrandmother's abdomen, which medics
OL,20,Fput down medication she was taking
OL,21,Ffollowing a heart valve replacement.
