OL,6,FShe was discharged, but returned to
OL,7,Fhospital in May 2021 when her symptoms
OL,8,Fgot worse, and was eventually
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with gastro-intestinal
OL,10,Fstromal tumour, a rare cancer of the
OL,11,Fdigestive system.
OL,13,FMrs Eastwood was told the cancer was
OL,14,Fterminal in January 2022 and died four
OL,15,Fmonths later.
OL,17,FMr Eastwood described his late wife as
OL,18,F"wonderful".
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@KO]
