OL,6,F"I feel absolutely disgusted with the
OL,7,F'care' she received from the
OL,8,Fhospital," he added.
OL,10,F"They didn't investigate the scan
OL,11,Fresults and just put it down to
OL,12,FWarfarin straight away.
OL,14,F"It seemed like the medical teams did
OL,15,Fnot communicate with each other and
OL,16,Feverything felt very disjointed.
OL,18,F"They left her in agony for months
OL,19,Fbefore she died."
