OL,6,FThe PHSO recently closed its
OL,7,Finvestigation on Mrs Eastwood's death,
OL,8,Fclaiming the delay meant she missed
OL,9,Fout on the chance of treatment which
OL,10,Fhad has 95% survival rate.
OL,12,FHer scans were not interpreted
OL,13,Fcorrectly, the probe found, and the
OL,14,Fimages should have been reviewed by a
OL,15,Fmulti-disciplinary, with further
OL,16,Finvestigations of the mass performed
OL,17,Fwithin three months.
